trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects, typically used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects for a connection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> classe é uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos, normalmente usados pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objeto para gerenciar um conjunto de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos para uma conexão.

trans-unit.source: The transformers related to a Web Parts connection can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Os transformadores relacionados a uma conexão de Web Parts podem ser recuperados por meio de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> a ser adicionado ao final do <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds an object to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um objeto ao fim da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The index at which <paramref name="transformer" /> has been added.
trans-unit.target: O índice no qual o <paramref name="transformer" /> foi adicionado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que é verificado para determinar se ele está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular transformer exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se um transformador específico existe na coleção.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular transformer is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um valor booliano que indica se um transformador específico está na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> método permite que você verifique se um determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> do objeto e determinar se ele é parte de um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> objeto.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz de objetos de <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> para conter a coleção copiada.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: O ponto inicial na matriz na qual o conteúdo da coleção será colocado.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Copia a coleção para uma matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> método é útil quando você deseja montar uma matriz personalizada que pode conter todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> coleção, um subconjunto desses objetos, ou um subconjunto desses objetos.
